you tend to, uh, let things go.

907
00:59:14,075 --> 00:59:16,305
啊，真是太可爱了
Aw, isn't that sweet?

908
00:59:16,344 --> 00:59:19,609
我发现过去流行的罗曼史是那么动人！
I find old-fashioned romance so touching, don't you?

909
00:59:19,648 --> 00:59:21,478
