哦，哦，哦！不！
Oh, uh, ooh. Uh, no.

911
00:59:23,716 --> 00:59:25,616
谢谢，我们不喝酒
Thank you, we don't drink...

912
00:59:25,652 --> 00:59:27,914
还有，我们不是夫妻
and, uh, we're not a couple.

913
00:59:29,988 --> 00:59:32,456
啊哈，看这些标记
Ahem. Look at these markings.

914
00:59:32,490 --> 00:59:35,822
和地图上的一模一样
They're identical to the ones on the map.

915
00:59:35,860 --> 00:59:39,757
我猜想这是远古文化中 的象形文字留下来的
I suspect these are the hieroglyphic remnants...of an ancient culture.

916
00:59:39,795 --> 00:59:41,286
霍金斯先生
Mr. Hawkins...

917
00:59:41,331 --> 00:59:44,266
别让任何人靠近
stop anyone who tries to approach. Ohh!

918
00:59:44,300 --> 00:59:45,857
