Yes, yes. Now listen to me...

919
00:59:45,900 --> 00:59:50,097
不要操心指挥的事， 安静的躺一会儿
stop giving orders for a few milliseconds and lie still.

920
00:59:50,138 --> 00:59:52,229
不错的建议，博士
Very forceful, Doctor.

921
00:59:52,272 --> 00:59:54,331
继续，说点别的
Go on. Say something else.

922
00:59:54,375 --> 00:59:54,545
嘿，看那儿，还有几个你们的朋友
Hey. Iook! There's some more of your buddies!

923
00:59:54,545 --> 00:59:57,775
嘿，看那儿，还有几个你们的朋友
Hey. Iook! There's some more of your buddies!

924
00:59:57,813 --> 01:00:00,782
