Hey, fellas! We're over here, fellas!

925
01:00:00,816 --> 01:00:03,908
哦哦哦！
Oh! Uhh! Ooh! Ohh!

926
01:00:05,986 --> 01:00:10,183
不要浪费子弹！
Stop wastin' your fire!

927
01:00:11,223 --> 01:00:13,715
你们好啊，上面的人！
Hello. up there!

928
01:00:16,227 --> 01:00:17,923
吉姆？
Jimbo?

929
01:00:17,963 --> 01:00:21,329
你和船长他们都好吗？
If it's all right with the captain...

930
01:00:21,365 --> 01:00:24,265
我跟你说句话
I'd like a short word with ya.

931
01:00:24,302 --> 01:00:27,895
不是圈套
No tricks,

932
01:00:27,936 --> 01:00:30,633
肯定是冲着地图来的
Come to bargain for the map, doubtless.

933
01:00:30,673 --> 01:00:31,800
这个垃圾...
Pestilential...

934
01:00:31,841 --> 01:00:33,900
-啊！ -船长
-Ugh! -Captain.

935
01:00:33,942 --> 01:00:39,379
那就是说， 他还以为地图在我们手上？
That means...that he thinks we still have it.

936
01:00:44,284 --> 01:00:50,221
啊，墨菲， 我还以为你跑哪儿去了呢
Ah, Morphy! I wondered where you was off to.

937
01:00:53,858 --> 01:00:55,086
哦
Ooh.

938
01:00:55,125 --> 01:00:58,423
哦，这条老腿
Oh, this poor old leg's downright snarky...

939
01:00:58,461 --> 01:01:01,430
我们在船上的那次 捉迷藏之后就不中用了
since that game attack we had in the galley.

940
01:01:03,532 --> 01:01:05,124
啊
Ahh.

941
01:01:07,201 --> 01:01:10,135
无论你在那里听到了什么
Whatever you heard back there...

942
01:01:10,170 --> 01:01:12,435
至少那些关于你的
at least the part concerning you...

943
01:01:12,473 --> 01:01:16,340
我说的都是实话
I didn't mean a word of it.

944
01:01:16,375 --> 01:01:20,504
那些残忍的家伙 都认为我变的心软了
Had that bloodthirsty lot thought I'd gone soft...

945
01:01:20,545 --> 01:01:22,978
