they'd have gutted us both.

946
01:01:25,116 --> 01:01:29,644
听着，如果我们处理得当
Listen to me. If we play our cards right...

947
01:01:29,685 --> 01:01:34,986
有了这些钱， 我们可以去当国王了
we can both walk away from this rich as kings.

948
01:01:35,024 --> 01:01:37,458
-是吗？ -呵呵呵
-Yeah? -Ha ha ha.

949
01:01:37,493 --> 01:01:40,586
你把地图给我
You get me that map...

950
01:01:40,629 --> 01:01:42,391
哦
and, uh...

951
01:01:42,429 --> 01:01:46,921
财宝中的很大一部分， 就是你的了
an even portion of the treasure is yours.

952
01:01:52,639 --> 01:01:54,970
孩子
Boy.

953
01:01:55,007 --> 01:02:00,404
