看着我，吉姆
Now, just see here, Jimbo--

956
01:02:05,915 --> 01:02:07,143
我想，至少
I mean, at least

957
01:02:07,182 --> 01:02:08,545
要坚持下去，是不是？
Stick to it, right?

958
01:02:08,583 --> 01:02:10,551
对了，那就是我要做的
Well, that's just what I'm gonna do.

959
01:02:10,585 --> 01:02:12,212
我会让你永远看不到
I'm gonna make sure that you never see...

960
01:02:12,254 --> 01:02:14,879
我的那些财宝
one drabloon of my treasure!

961
01:02:14,921 --> 01:02:18,449
那些财宝是属于我的！
That treasure is owed me,

962
01:02:18,492 --> 01:02:22,860
好了，那你就试着 不要用我的地图，去找到它吧
Well, try to find it without my map, by thunder!

963
01:02:22,894 --> 01:02:27,989
哦，你还不知道 怎么发挥你的斗志是不是？
Oh, you still don't know how to pick your fights, do you, boy?

964
01:02:28,031 --> 01:02:31,469
好，看着我
Now, mark me.

965
01:02:31,503 --> 01:02:35,129
你有两个选择： 天亮之前把地图给我
Either I get that map by dawn tomorrow...

966
01:02:35,171 --> 01:02:39,301
