or so help me, I'll use the ship's cannons...

967
01:02:39,341 --> 01:02:43,140
把你们炸烂！
to blast ya all to kingdom come!

968
01:02:43,178 --> 01:02:46,203
墨菲，跟我走
Morph, hop to it.

969
01:02:47,581 --> 01:02:49,047
马上过来！
Now!

970
01:02:51,618 --> 01:02:53,381
哦，见鬼！
Oh, blast it!

971
01:03:05,027 --> 01:03:06,825
先生们
Gentlemen...

972
01:03:06,863 --> 01:03:10,798
我们必须呆在一起， 还有...
we must stay together and...

973
01:03:10,833 --> 01:03:12,664
还有...哦
and...ohh.

974
01:03:12,702 --> 01:03:14,497
还有什么？什么？
And what? What?!

975
01:03:14,536 --> 01:03:17,061
我们必须呆在一起， 还有什么？
We must stay together and what?!

976
01:03:17,105 --> 01:03:22,598
博士，你的眼睛真迷人
Doctor,

977
01:03:22,642 --> 01:03:24,236
她已经神智不清了
She's lost her mind!

978
01:03:24,278 --> 01:03:25,505
哦，你应该赶紧帮帮她
Well, you gotta help her.

979
01:03:25,545 --> 01:03:27,875
该死，吉姆，我是个 天文学家，不是医生
Dang it, Jim. I'm an astronomer, not a doctor.

980
01:03:27,913 --> 01:03:30,279
我是说，我是个博士
I mean, I am a doctor,

981
01:03:30,315 --> 01:03:31,941
我有博士头衔， 但那不是一回事儿
I have a doctorate. It's not the same thing.

982
01:03:31,983 --> 01:03:33,450
这博士头衔救不了人
You can't help people with a doctorate.

983
01:03:33,484 --> 01:03:36,009
你怎么只是坐在那里， 也不来帮忙？
You just sit there, and you're useless.

984
01:03:36,052 --> 01:03:38,315
好了，博士
It's OK, Doc.

985
01:03:38,355 --> 01:03:40,082
没事的
It's all right.

986
01:03:40,122 --> 01:03:43,525
是的，博士！ 吉姆知道怎么离开这里。
Yeah, Doc! Jimmy knows exactly how to get out of this.

987
01:03:43,560 --> 01:03:46,686
只有吉姆能想到这些办法
It's just Jimmy has this knowledge of things.

988
01:03:46,793 --> 01:03:50,355
吉姆，有主意了吗？
Jim, any thoughts at all?

989
01:03:50,398 --> 01:03:53,491
没有地图，我们就完蛋了
Without the map, we're dead.

990
01:03:54,668 --> 01:03:57,500
我们想要逃走， 肯定是死
If we try to leave, we're dead.

991
01:03:57,536 --> 01:03:59,526
-呆在这里... -我们死定了
-lf we stay here-- -We're dead!

992
01:03:59,572 --> 01:04:01,039
我们死定了！我们死定了！
We're dead! We're dead!

993
01:04:05,210 --> 01:04:09,838
好了，我想吉姆要静下来想想。
Well, I think that Jimmy could use a little quiet time. Heh.

994
01:04:09,879 --> 01:04:13,109
所以，我要从后门出去了
So I'll just slip out the back door.

995
01:04:13,149 --> 01:04:15,343
-后门？ -是的
-Back door? -Oh, yeah.

996
01:04:15,383 --> 01:04:17,543
我从这儿可以轻松逃走
I get this delightful breeze through here...

997
01:04:17,586 --> 01:04:18,848
我想这很重要
which I think is important...

998
01:04:18,887 --> 01:04:20,285
因为在朋友之间活动...
because ventilation among friends--

999
01:04:20,321 --> 01:04:22,881
哇，这是什么？
Whoa. What is all this stuff?

1000
01:04:22,922 --> 01:04:25,186
你是说那些远处的机器
You mean the miles and miles of machinery that run...

1001
01:04:25,226 --> 01:04:27,455
在行星中是怎么运转的吗？
through the entire course of the inside of this planet?

1002
01:04:27,493 --> 01:04:29,188
你在说什么？
Not a clue.

1003
01:04:29,229 --> 01:04:31,629
博士，博士， 我想我找到出口了
Hey, Doc! Doc! I think I found a way out of here!

1004
01:04:31,664 --> 01:04:34,130
不，不，吉姆，等等 船长让我们呆在一起
No, no. Jim, wait.

1005
01:04:34,165 --> 01:04:37,064
-我会回来的 -冲啊！
-I'll be back. -Cannonball!

1006
01:04:37,100 --> 01:04:38,692
呜呼！
Woof.

1007
01:04:46,941 --> 01:04:49,466
-有什么计划？ -嘘，本，安静！
-So, what's the plan? -Shh. B.E.N., quiet.

1008
01:04:53,581 --> 01:04:54,945
好了，是这样
OK, here it is.

1009
01:04:54,983 --> 01:04:58,509
我们偷偷回到船上， 毁掉激光炮
We sneak back to the Legacy, disable the laser cannons...

1010
01:04:58,550 --> 01:05:00,213
把地图带回来
and bring back the map.

1011
01:05:00,254 --> 01:05:01,481
计划听起来很不错
That's a good plan.

1012
01:05:01,520 --> 01:05:03,111
我喜欢。 只是..
I like that plan. The only thing is...

1013
01:05:03,153 --> 01:05:05,587
我想我们要怎么回去？
I'm wondering, how do we get there?

1014
01:05:05,624 --> 01:05:07,056
用那个
On that.

1015
