就是你了
Yes.

1027
01:05:59,667 --> 01:06:01,463
坏了，本，坏事了
Bad, B.E.N. Bad.

1028
01:06:01,500 --> 01:06:02,626
好了，修好了
OK, fixing.

1029
01:06:02,669 --> 01:06:05,638
那愚蠢的机器人 会害死我们的
That stupid robot's gonna get us all...killed.

1030
01:06:05,672 --> 01:06:07,934
服务生！
Cabin boy.

1031
01:06:16,480 --> 01:06:17,809
啊！
Aah!

1032
01:06:35,294 --> 01:06:37,694
喔，OK，不着急
Whoops. OK. don't panic.

1033
01:06:37,729 --> 01:06:40,059
吸气，呼气
Breathing in... breathing out...

1034
