Gee, that wasn't so tough.

1053
01:08:21,517 --> 01:08:23,246
博士，博士！醒醒！
Doc! Doc, wake up!

1054
01:08:23,285 --> 01:08:26,482
我找到地图了
I got the map.

1055
01:08:26,521 --> 01:08:31,788
干得好，吉姆 谢谢你帮我
Fine work, Jimbo.

1056
01:08:35,929 --> 01:08:38,725
孩子，谢谢你帮我们找到那条路
Thanks for showing us the way, boy.

1057
01:08:42,168 --> 01:08:44,066
啊！
Aah!

1058
01:08:46,837 --> 01:08:49,238
这堆烂铁是什么玩意儿？
What's this sorry stack of metal?!

1059
01:08:49,273 --> 01:08:50,570
不要碰我的脸！
Not the face!

1060
01:08:50,607 --> 01:08:53,475
吉姆，你跟我一样
You're just like me, Jimbo.

1061
01:08:53,511 --> 01:08:56,603
你讨厌失败
Ya hates to lose.

1062
