Oh, the powers that be. Would you look?

1066
01:09:48,586 --> 01:09:50,780
哈哈哈哈
Ha ha ha ha!

1067
01:09:50,822 --> 01:09:54,814
绑紧他让他们一起呆着， 直到我们...什么？
Tie him up and leave him with the others till we--what?

1068
01:09:55,891 --> 01:09:57,450
你要地图
You want the map...

1069
01:09:57,493 --> 01:09:59,325
