We'll take 'em all.

1072
01:10:20,878 --> 01:10:22,642
哦
Unh.

1073
01:10:31,489 --> 01:10:34,184
没事，墨菲，没事的
It's OK, Morph. It's OK.

1074
01:10:34,222 --> 01:10:36,122
吉米，我不知道你为什么...
Jimmy, l--I don't know about you...

1075
01:10:36,158 --> 01:10:39,990
我看到我的一生在我眼前滑过
but I'm starting to see my life pass in front of my eyes.

1076
01:10:40,027 --> 01:10:42,017
至少，那是我的一生
At least, I think it's my life.

1077
01:10:42,062 --> 01:10:45,190
我和一个叫着卢皮的机器人跳过舞？
Was I ever dancing with an android named Lupe?!

1078
01:10:45,231 --> 01:10:47,358
本，嘘
B.E.N., shh.

1079
01:10:47,400 --> 01:10:49,559
