1083
01:11:02,944 --> 01:11:05,004
在哪儿？
Where is it?

1084
01:11:05,046 --> 01:11:09,540
我什么都没看到！ 狗屎，怎么什么都没有？
I see nothing! One great, big stinking hunk of nothing!

1085
01:11:09,584 --> 01:11:12,485
