What's going on, Jimbo?

1086
01:11:12,520 --> 01:11:15,386
我不知道， 我打不开了
I don't know. I can't get it open.

1087
01:11:15,421 --> 01:11:18,118
我们早就不该跟着这小子了！
We should've never followed this boy!

1088
01:11:18,157 --> 01:11:19,591
嘿！
Hey!

1089
01:11:19,626 --> 01:11:21,389
我劝你最好
I'd suggest you get...

1090
01:11:21,427 --> 01:11:23,554
把那东西弄好！快点！
that gizmo going again. and fast!

1091
01:11:23,596 --> 01:11:26,893
把他杀了，剖开他的肚子！
Let's rip his gizzard right out right now!

1092
01:11:26,930 --> 01:11:29,558
把他从山崖上扔下去！
Throw him off the cliff!

1093
01:11:50,649 --> 01:11:53,049
哦，原谅他吧
Oh, have mercy.

1094
01:11:54,487 --> 01:11:56,851
星云图？
The Lagoon Nebula?

1095
01:11:56,887 --> 01:12:00,449
那只是星系中的一部分
But that's halfway across the galaxy.

1096
01:12:02,159 --> 01:12:04,627
有个大门
A big door...

1097
01:12:04,661 --> 01:12:06,788
开开关关
opening and closing.

1098
01:12:10,698 --> 01:12:12,495
让我看看
Let's see.

1099
01:12:12,534 --> 01:12:15,991
金纳皮斯（地名）
Kinapis.

1100
01:12:16,037 --> 01:12:17,663
蒙特里莎空间站
Montressor spaceport.

1101
01:12:20,873 --> 01:12:22,841
弗林特就是这么做的
So that's how Flint did it.

1102
01:12:22,875 --> 01:12:28,073
他用这个入口 到世界各地去掠夺财宝的！
He used this portal to roam the universe stealing treasure.

1103
01:12:28,113 --> 01:12:30,513
他把它们都藏到哪儿去了呢？
But where'd he stash it all?

1104
01:12:31,781 --> 01:12:34,944
那个该死的财宝在哪儿？
Where's that blasted treasure?!

1105
01:12:34,984 --> 01:12:37,145
财宝！财宝！
Treasure! Treasure!

1106
01:12:37,187 --> 01:12:39,177
它被埋在...
It's buried in the--

1107
01:12:39,221 --> 01:12:43,555
埋在机器的中央核心处
Buried in the centroid of the mechanism.

1108
01:12:43,592 --> 01:12:47,391
如果这个行星就是那个机器
What if the whole planet is the mechanism...

1109
01:12:47,428 --> 01:12:51,692
财宝就埋在行星的中央
and the treasure is buried in the center of this planet?

1110
01:12:55,402 --> 01:12:58,426
太令人失望了， 我们怎么样才能到那里？
And how in blue blazes are we supposed to get there?

1111
01:12:58,470 --> 01:13:01,927
只要打开右边的门就可以了
Just open the right door.

1112
01:13:18,657 --> 01:13:21,953
等等我！等等我！
Wait for me! Wait for me!

1113
01:13:30,699 --> 01:13:35,102
从数千个世界掠夺来的战利品
The loot of a thousand worlds.

1114
01:13:38,071 --> 01:13:41,234
我们要一只更大的船！
We are going to need a bigger boat!

1115
01:13:53,684 --> 01:13:56,981
这怎么看起来这么眼熟？
This is all seeming very familiar.

1116
01:13:59,020 --> 01:14:02,616
为什么？
I can't remember why.

1117
01:14:02,657 --> 01:14:03,954
本，跟我来
B.E.N., come on.

1118
01:14:03,992 --> 01:14:06,426
我们离开这里， 但不能空手离开
We're getting out of here, and we're not leaving empty-handed.

1119
01:14:06,461 --> 01:14:08,620
但是，但是，吉米，吉米！
But--but, Jimmy! Jimmy!

1120
01:14:10,029 --> 01:14:13,658
我这一生的追求
A lifetime of searching.

1121
01:14:13,700 --> 01:14:16,759
最后
And at long last...

1122
01:14:17,869 --> 01:14:20,633
我终于找到了
I can touch it.

1123
01:14:20,671 --> 01:14:21,865
你没觉得奇怪吗？
Do you know what's strange?

1124
01:14:21,906 --> 01:14:23,806
我没法阻止这件事情发生，吉米
I can't tell you how frustrating this is, Jimmy...

1125
01:14:23,841 --> 01:14:25,330
因为有些想法...
'cause there's something just--

1126
01:14:25,374 --> 01:14:27,466
在我的脑子里盘旋不去
it's nagging at the back of my mind.

1127
01:14:27,510 --> 01:14:29,206
啊！
Aah!

1128
01:14:29,246 --> 01:14:32,736
-弗林特船长？ -还是个人形！
-Captain Flint? -ln the flesh!

1129
01:14:32,781 --> 01:14:36,580
哦，还保持完好
Well, s-sort of,

1130
01:14:36,618 --> 01:14:39,313
或者说是像个人形
or anything that--that--that resembles flesh...

1131
01:14:39,353 --> 01:14:41,343
不是的
that's not there.

1132
01:14:41,387 --> 01:14:43,447
怎么这么奇怪？ 你看出来了吗？
And yet it's so odd. you know?

1133
01:14:43,490 --> 01:14:46,550
我记得有些很恐怖的事
I remember there was something horrible...

1134
01:14:46,592 --> 01:14:48,652
弗林特不想任何人知道...
Flint didn't want anyone else to know...

1135
01:14:48,694 --> 01:14:52,686
但是我就是想不起来是什么
but I--I just can't remember what it was.

1136
01:14:52,731 --> 01:14:56,096
哦，一件很恐怖的事情...
Oh, a mind

1137
01:14:58,268 --> 01:15:00,758
本，我想我找到你的脑子了
B.E.N.,

1138
01:15:00,803 --> 01:15:01,997
别动
Hold still.

1139
01:15:02,037 --> 01:15:05,233
啊！吉米，你的手太冰了
Aah! Jimmy, your hands are very, very cold.

1140
01:15:07,008 --> 01:15:08,736
哇！
Whoa!

1141
01:15:08,776 --> 01:15:10,676
你好啊
Hello.

1142
01:15:10,711 --> 01:15:13,305
哦，吉米，我在想...
You know, uh, Jimmy, I was just thinking...

1143
01:15:13,347 --> 01:15:15,872
我在想...
I was just think--

1144
01:15:15,915 --> 01:15:18,941
我的记忆全回来了
It's all flooding back! All my memories!

1145
01:15:18,985 --> 01:15:20,713
对了，弗林特把我的存储器电路拔下来
Right up until Flint pulled my memory circuits...

1146
01:15:20,753 --> 01:15:23,654
我就无法告诉 别人他设下的陷阱！
so I could never tell anybody about his booby trap!

1147
01:15:24,922 --> 01:15:27,914
-说什么？ -啊？
-Speaking of which... -Huh?

1148
01:15:29,860 --> 01:15:30,986
弗林特要保证...
Flint wanted to make sure...

1149
01:15:31,027 --> 01:15:32,426
没人可以偷走他的财宝
that nobody could ever steal his treasure...

1150
01:15:32,462 --> 01:15:33,723
所以，他控制了整个行星
so he rigged this whole planet...

1151
01:15:33,763 --> 01:15:37,061
它会把你炸得比卡勒希安风筝还高
to blow higher than a Kalepsian kite!

1152
01:15:47,841 --> 01:15:49,740
快跑，吉米！快逃命吧！
Run, Jimmy! Run for your life!

1153
01:15:49,776 --> 01:15:51,300
你回去帮船长和博士！
You go back and help the captain and Doc!

1154
01:15:51,343 --> 01:15:54,675
如果我5分钟之后还没回去 你们就先走
If I'm not there in 5 minutes,

1155
01:15:54,712 --> 01:15:57,873
我不会离开我的朋友，吉米
I am not leaving my buddy Jimmy.

1156
01:15:57,915 --> 01:16:01,042
除非他这么看着我
Unless he looks at me like that.

1157
01:16:01,084 --> 01:16:02,414
再见，吉姆
Bye, Jim!

1158
01:16:08,924 --> 01:16:12,325
不！不！哦！不！哦！不！
No! No! Oh, no! Oh, no!

1159
01:16:12,359 --> 01:16:13,485
不！啊！
No! Aah!

1160
01:16:15,262 --> 01:16:18,992
-啊！ -啊！
-Aah! -Aah!

1161
01:16:22,968 --> 01:16:25,697
回来，笨蛋！
Come back here, ya blighters!

1162
01:16:41,150 --> 01:16:45,482
我这一生都想要 一次像这样的冒险
All my life, I dreamed of an adventure like this.

1163
01:16:45,520 --> 01:16:47,510
哦，对不起
I'm just sorry...

1164
01:16:47,555 --> 01:16:50,751
我不能好好的帮你
I couldn't have been more helpful to you.

1165
01:16:50,790 --> 01:16:52,758
哦，别傻了
Oh, don't be daft.

1166
01:16:52,792 --> 01:16:56,521
其实，你已经帮了我很多
You've been very helpful. Truly.

1167
01:16:56,562 --> 01:17:01,760
我觉得自己就像 一个无能的家伙
I feel like such a useless weakling...

1168
01:17:01,799 --> 01:17:04,359
我没用多大劲啊
with abnormally thin wrists.

1169
01:17:04,400 --> 01:17:06,595
对不起，海盗先生
Excuse me, brutish pirate.

1170
01:17:07,803 --> 01:17:09,600
对了，就是你，我有个问题
Yes, you. I have a question.

1171
01:17:09,639 --> 01:17:11,869
你的身材对于你那小小的脑袋
Is it that your body is too massive...

1172
01:17:11,907 --> 01:17:13,431
是不是太过于臃肿了？
for your teeny-tiny head...

1173
01:17:13,475 --> 01:17:15,908
或者说是你的脑袋对于你壮硕的身躯
or is it that your head is too teeny-tiny...

1174
01:17:15,944 --> 01:17:18,811
太过渺小了？
for your big, fat body?

1175
01:17:18,847 --> 01:17:20,938
我要好好教训你！
I pummel you good!

1176
01:17:20,981 --> 01:17:23,280
是的，我想你会这么做的。 但这之前
Yes, I'm sure you will, but before you do...

1177
01:17:23,317 --> 01:17:26,341
我还有一个问题。 这是你的吗？
I have one more question. Is this yours?

1178
01:17:26,385 --> 01:17:27,785
哦
Uhh...

1179
01:17:34,592 --> 01:17:36,787
是的！墨菲， 我们就要出去了！
Yes! Morph, we are so out of here!

1180
01:17:38,295 --> 01:17:39,784
啊，吉姆！
Ah. Jimbo!

1181
01:17:40,997 --> 01:17:44,830
你真是世界的第七大奇迹！
Aren't you the seventh wonder of the universe?

1182
01:17:44,867 --> 01:17:47,301
退回去！
Get back!

1183
01:17:51,405 --> 01:17:55,340
我喜欢你，小伙子 我远道而来
I like you, lad, but I've come too far...

1184
01:17:55,375 --> 01:17:57,740
你却阻扰我拿回我的财宝
to let you stand between me and me treasure.

1185
01:18:02,813 --> 01:18:04,440
啊！
Aah!

1186
01:18:17,659 --> 01:18:20,355
哦，不，哦，不要！
Oh, no, you don't!

1187
01:18:29,069 --> 01:18:30,263
什么？
What?

1188
01:18:34,406 --> 01:18:35,805
吉姆
Jimbo.

1189
01:18:38,675 --> 01:18:40,802
抓住了
Reach for me now!

1190
01:18:40,843 --> 01:18:43,811
抓住！
Reach!

1191
01:18:43,845 --> 01:18:45,608
我...我够不着！
I--I can't!

1192
01:18:45,647 --> 01:18:48,207
啊！
Aah!

1193
01:18:54,423 --> 01:18:56,116
我...
I...

1194
01:19:00,693 --> 01:19:05,823
哦，我简直就是个疯子！
Oh, blast me for a fool!

1195
01:19:05,863 --> 01:19:07,387
啊！
Aah!

1196
01:19:28,591 --> 01:19:30,388
席尔瓦，你放弃了？
Silver, you gave up?

1197
01:19:30,427 --> 01:19:34,294
它困扰了我一生，吉姆！ 我会克服的！
Just a lifelong obsession, Jim. I'll get over it.

1198
01:19:34,330 --> 01:19:36,161
欢迎你回来，吉米！
Aloha. Jimmy!

1199
01:19:38,467 --> 01:19:40,298
快点！只剩2分34秒
Hurry, people! We got exactly two minutes...

1200
01:19:40,335 --> 01:19:43,324
行星就要爆炸了
and thirty-four seconds till planet's destruction!

1201
01:19:43,369 --> 01:19:44,667
做的很好，博士
You're doing fine, Doctor.

1202
01:19:44,704 --> 01:19:46,934
现在让它放松一点， 慢慢来，慢慢来！
Now ease her over gently--gently!

1203
01:19:48,307 --> 01:19:52,504
啊！我们呆在行星上都比这好
Aah! We were better off on exploding planet!

1204
01:19:54,879 --> 01:19:56,744
赶紧让我们离开这里，金属人！
Take us out of here, metal man!

1205
01:19:56,780 --> 01:19:58,271
遵命，船长
Aye, Captain!

1206
01:20:01,884 --> 01:20:04,682
船长，你简直就是神女下凡...
Captain, you dropped from the heavens in the nick of--

1207
01:20:04,720 --> 01:20:07,448
把讨好的话跟法官说吧，席尔瓦
Save your claptrap for the judge, Silver!

1208
01:20:17,865 --> 01:20:19,525
导弹尾部被破坏了
Missile tail demobilized,

1209
01:20:19,565 --> 01:20:21,328
推进器只剩30％的能量
Thrusters at only 30% of capacity.

1210
01:20:21,367 --> 01:20:23,301
30％？就是说，我们...
30%? That means we're--

1211
01:20:23,335 --> 01:20:26,428
我们无法在行星爆炸之前离开了
We'll never clear the planet's explosion in time.

1212
01:20:34,310 --> 01:20:37,211
-调头回去。 -什么？
-We gotta turn around. -What?

1213
01:20:37,246 --> 01:20:40,146
那里有个入口， 我们可以从那里离开
There's a portal back there. It can get us out of here!

1214
01:20:40,182 --> 01:20:42,479
对不起，吉姆。 那个入口还没打开
Pardon me. Jim. but didn't that portal open...

1215
01:20:42,518 --> 01:20:44,677
回到火一般的地狱？
onto a raging inferno?!

1216
01:20:44,718 --> 01:20:47,687
是的，我要把更改入口
Yes, but I'm gonna change that.

1217
01:20:47,721 --> 01:20:50,382
打开另外一个门
I'm gonna open a different door.

1218
01:20:51,724 --> 01:20:53,022
船长，真的吗？ 我觉得那太不可思议
Captain, really, I don't see how this is possible--

1219
01:20:53,059 --> 01:20:55,219
照着他说的做
Listen to the boy!

1220
01:20:55,260 --> 01:20:57,819
离行星爆炸还有1分20秒
One minute, twenty-nine seconds till planet's destruction!

1221
01:20:57,861 --> 01:21:01,354
-我们还要怎么做？吉姆？ -想想怎么绑住这东西！
-What do you need, Jim? -Just some way to attach this.

1222
01:21:01,399 --> 01:21:03,889
好的，后退，后退一点！
All right. Stand back. Stand back, now.

1223
01:21:05,502 --> 01:21:07,731
可以走了
There you go.

1224
01:21:07,769 --> 01:21:08,963
可以走了
There you go.

1225
01:21:10,072 --> 01:21:12,472
好了，不管发生什么
OK. Now,

1226
01:21:12,508 --> 01:21:14,973
把飞船直接冲向入口
keep the ship heading straight for that portal.

1227
01:21:15,009 --> 01:21:17,875
还剩58秒
Fifty-eight seconds!

1228
01:21:24,750 --> 01:21:26,842
好了，你们听到他说的了
Well, you heard him!

1229
01:21:26,884 --> 01:21:30,217
调头
Get this blasted heap turned 'round!

1230
01:21:31,288 --> 01:21:32,812
博士，把船头对准入口
Doctor,

1231
01:21:32,856 --> 01:21:34,222
遵命，船长
Aye, Captain.

1232
01:21:56,808 --> 01:21:58,571
向右，右边！
Go to the right! The right!

1233
01:21:58,609 --> 01:22:02,205
我知道，我知道！ 我只是在试试
I know, I know!

1234
01:22:04,415 --> 01:22:06,281
25秒！
Twenty-five seconds!

1235
01:22:11,221 --> 01:22:12,653
不！不！
No! No!

1236
01:22:16,124 --> 01:22:17,921
加油，小伙子！
Come on, lad.

1237
01:22:19,393 --> 01:22:22,226
17秒！
Seventeen seconds!

1238
01:22:37,275 --> 01:22:38,604
7...
Seven...

1239
01:22:38,641 --> 01:22:41,702
6...5...4...
six... five... four...

1240
01:22:41,744 --> 01:22:44,269
3...2...
three...two...

1241
01:22:52,353 --> 01:22:55,343
哇！吔！
Wow! Y eah!

1242
01:22:55,388 --> 01:22:58,379
你成功了，吉米！
You done it. Jimmy!

1243
01:22:58,424 --> 01:23:02,019
你成功了！哈哈哈！
You done it, boy! Ha ha ha!

1244
01:23:02,060 --> 01:23:04,654
我早说过了这孩子很出色！
Didn't I say the lad had greatness in him?

1245
01:23:16,905 --> 01:23:20,601
太好了
Unorthodox,

1246
01:23:20,642 --> 01:23:22,507
我很荣幸把你推荐给
I'd be proud to recommend you...

1247
01:23:22,543 --> 01:23:26,240
星际学院， 他们需要一个像你这样的人
to the interstellar academy. They could use a man like you.

1248
01:23:26,278 --> 01:23:29,214
等着吧， 你妈妈听到这个肯定很高兴！
Just wait until your mother hears about this!

1249
01:23:29,249 --> 01:23:31,408
那当然，我们不用再为生计犯愁了
Of course, we may downplay the life-threatening parts.

1250
01:23:31,450 --> 01:23:35,319
吉米，这真是终生难忘的时刻
Jimmy, that was unforgettable!

1251
01:23:35,354 --> 01:23:36,650
我知道你不喜欢我碰你
I know you don't like touching...

1252
01:23:36,687 --> 01:23:39,918
但是，准备好， 我要好好的拥抱你
but get ready for a hug, big guy, 'cause I gotta hug ya!

1253
01:23:39,958 --> 01:23:41,151
哈哈哈！
Ha ha ha ha!

1254
01:23:43,127 --> 01:23:45,423
嘿，你也回过来抱我了
Hey, you hugged me back.

1255
01:23:45,461 --> 01:23:48,259
哦，我发誓不再哭的
Oh, I promised myself I wouldn't cry.

1256
01:23:54,502 --> 01:23:57,470
你们谁有纸巾？
Does anyone have a tissue?

1257
01:23:58,913 --> 01:24:02,075
-墨菲，我们做标记！ -我知道
-Morphy, we gotta make tracks. -I know.

1258
01:24:02,115 --> 01:24:04,378
你不会离开的，是不是？
You never quit. do you?

1259
01:24:04,417 --> 01:24:07,145
啊，吉姆！哈哈
Ah, Jimbo! Ha ha!

1260
01:24:07,185 --> 01:24:09,246
我只是检查一下，看看...
I was merely checking to make sure...

1261
01:24:09,287 --> 01:24:12,414
看看我们最后 一艘船是不是完好无损！
our last longboat was safe and secure.

1262
01:24:13,558 --> 01:24:16,026
呣！
Mmm.

1263
01:24:16,059 --> 01:24:17,218
哦
Well...

1264
01:24:18,829 --> 01:24:19,988
应该绑紧了
that should hold it.

1265
01:24:20,029 --> 01:24:23,520
呵呵，我教得很好啊
Heh heh heh. I taught you too well.

1266
01:24:25,567 --> 01:24:29,058
如果你不介意， 我可不想进监狱
If you don't mind, we'd just as soon avoid prison.

1267
01:24:29,103 --> 01:24:34,199
小墨菲在这里自由自在
Little morphy here, he's a free spirit.

